Datasets that can be accessed via a function

These datasets should be accessed via the functions. i.e. you should not use these datasets directly unless you know what you are doing and have a specific purpose in mind.

These functions and datasets are out of date, and there are replacements available. Look at the “recommended functions and datasets” section and use those functions/datasets instead.
